---
description: How to use installed project skills
alwaysApply: true
---

This repo includes optional skills in `.cursor/skills/`.

Use skills only when relevant:
- `coding-guidelines` for implementation tasks, code changes, bug fixes, or feature development
- `clean-code-review` for readability review
- `refactoring-pass` for behavior-preserving refactoring
- `security-review` for risky code, dependencies, scripts, HTML rendering, or publishing

Do not load or apply every skill globally.
Do not run scripts from third-party skills unless the user explicitly approves.
